explanation: [0-0] In an indoor setting, two female workers are packing round eggplants. The worker wearing a headscarf is taking an eggplant from a bucket, preparing to pack it. The worker on the right, wearing white, is organizing a plastic basket full of wrapping paper, ready to receive the packed eggplants. Behind them are rows of buckets filled with eggplants.

[0-8] Subsequently, the worker wearing a headscarf places the eggplant on the white wrapping paper. The worker in white wraps the eggplant with the paper and puts it in the plastic basket.
